到吹噓自己既性別比異性好，然後夾硬整一套theory出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce99e01a3d95b415b35afe9a542b891d977538b","tid":15580,"uid":16029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢套陽具嫉妒理論真係呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n女權丁丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩係wiki初步睇完都覺得佢係痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後又有另外一個女性心理學家，叫霍妮<br />\n去講話其實男人都想做女人<br />\n因為男人冇得生仔而自卑 <br />\n所以先咁aggersive咁係自己既長處發揮黎彌補呢個自卑感<br />\n<br />\nwtf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本係兩個痴線佬係到吹噓自己既性別比異性好，然後夾硬整一套theory出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n霍妮與阿德勒都對弗洛伊德這樣的理論提出了不同意見。阿德勒認為女孩希望成為男孩是因為希望擁有那些被我們的文化認為屬於男孩的特質或特權，比如力量、勇氣、獨立、成功、性自由及選擇伴侶的權利這些文化因素而非生物因素即並非對陰莖本身的羨慕。霍妮則在之後的一篇論文中提到當男孩發現自己沒有懷孕生育的本能時[1]，他們反而會產生妒忌及自卑，所以男孩表現出的進取心，爭取成功是對這種自卑感的補償。"},{"pid":"e420c31e26aa936ff1e2de4e1b2e243778ecba99","tid":15580,"uid":46873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:02:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">二千幾年前</span>就已經建立到一套好完整既心理學出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未來撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\